<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10404511>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Coenosia spp. A–C. Coenosia nevaedensis. A. Terminalia, lateral view. B. Cercal plate, dorsal view. C. Sternite 5. D. Coenosia nigrotincta, terminalia, lateral view. E, F. Coenosia ukokensis. E. Terminalia, lateral view. F. Cercal plate, dorsal view. G. Coenosia apukaensis, terminalia, lateral view. H. Coenosia xuei, terminalia, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10404511/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10404519>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Coenosia spp. A, B. Coenosia ciliata. A. Male habitus, lateral view. B. Female habitus, lateral view. C. Coenosia penicillata, male habitus, lateral view. D, E. Coenosia subgracilis. D. Male habitus, lateral view (the holotype of Coenosia altaica Sorokina, 2009). E. Female habitus, lateral view (the paratype of C. altaica Sorokina, 2009). F, G. Coenosia oralis. F. Male habitus, lateral view. G. Female habitus, lateral view; H, I. Coenosia ukokensis. H. Male, holotype, lateral view. I. Female, paratype, lateral view. Bare: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10404519/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10404525>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Coenosia spp. A, B. Coenosia ozerovi. A. Male habitus, lateral view. B. Female habitus, lateral view. C, D. Coenosia nigrotincta. C. Female habitus, lateral view (Pevek). D. Male habitus, lateral view (Beringovskii). E, F. Coenosia ukokensis. E. Male habitus, lateral view (Magadan). F. Female habitus, lateral view (Magadan). Bare: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10404525/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

